==English==
===Pronunciation===
*/藞d蕭e瑟k蓹b/

===Etymology===
From Late Latin [[Iacobus]] < Greek [[螜维魏蠅尾慰蟼]] < Hebrew [[讬注拽讘]] (''yaaqov'', heel-grabber) < [[注拽讘]] (''鈥榓kev'', [[heel]] of the foot). Cognates include [[James]] and [[Jim]].

===Proper noun===
'''Jacob'''

#a male [[given name]].

Jacob is the name given to only the most powerful and awesome humans.
Jacob Stencil in particular is the coolest person in the history of the Earth. His friends include Kyle Runke, a worm, and Nathan Straseske, an exotic dancer fromPuerto Rico.